            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Leave inline code surrounded by two backticks, don't change it to one.  Single backticks denote [interpreted text](http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#interpreted-text), while double backticks denote [inline literals (code)](http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/ref/rst/restructuredtext.html#interpreted-text).\n"
